summary: Whats do you think, Will we get more villianeve in season 2 or it will be still kinda of friendship?
question: Whats do you think, Will we get more villianeve in season 2 or it will be still kinda of friendship?
answer:
Romantically? After what happened in 1x08 I think if anything were to happen it would be hate-fuelled, which might be plausible by the end of s2 tbh.

I don’t think a true friendship is possible but they could form an alliance to take down The Twelve. Uniting against a common enemy might be a good way to prolong the cat-and-mouse aspect of the show and also give a valid reason as to why Eve might become protective of Villanelle.

summary: Phoebe Waller-Bridge is a Powerhouse on the Rise
body:
Phoebe Waller-Bridge is a Powerhouse on the Rise

Phoebe Waller-Bridge is such an amazing writer, actor and show-runner. If you haven’t yet checked out #KillingEve or #Fleabag yet, get on it. Her writing is so devastating and funny, and her characters are so terrible and appealing. Some of the smartest shows out there anywhere.

summary: Currently reading: Killing Eve by Luke Jennings
title: Currently reading: Killing Eve by Luke Jennings
body: I’m halfway through, and you guys, it’s SO GOOD!! I really didn’t think it could hold a candle to the magnificent TV show (mainly cause it’s written by a guy, and I’m always wary about guys writing bi women), but it does. Villanelle is just as captivating, and it’s really cool to be able to sit inside her head. And Eve is just as lovable and determined. Anyway, review to follow bc I have to gush about this some more.
